nodevitals imports node_exporter's `collector` package so a single agent can
serve the full node_* metric surface with identical names, labels, and
semantics. Reimplementing those collectors would have re-derived years of
kernel-version edge cases and produced a schema that silently disagrees with
the ecosystem's. The Apache-2.0 terms above apply to that bundled portion;
nodevitals' own code remains MIT (see LICENSE).
